description:
Esther Povitsky [Crazy Ex-Girlfriend, Alone Together, Dollface]  is a writer, comedian, actor, and producer. Esther tells Anna about her dream to live in a shed behind her parent's house, how she approaches every day as if it were a Seinfeld episode, what it’s like having the same name as your 97-year-old grandma, and more.
